Hi team,

I’m getting this weaviate error on my sandbox, would someone know how to resolve this issue?

2025/07/16 19:17:37 ERROR weaviate/main.go:43 -- Failed to create DBSession for HA lease backend.
2025/07/16 19:17:37 FATAL weaviate/main.go:80 -- failed to get initlaize the db accessor: Empty DBParam string
make: *** [Makefile:19: run-docker] Error 1```
Sandbox link: https://instabase.sandboxes.site/sandboxes/gananprabaharan?cw=dev
Weaviate logs: https://instabase.sandboxes.site/logviewx/instabase/gananprabaharan/dev/daemon/weaviate%40instabase

CC:@anshul.padhi @Atinder
Have you tried resyncing your sandbox with a base refresh? I think this error occurs if you have a really old sandbox
Yeah I saw some threads about that, but I created this sandbox today, so assumed that wouldn’t be it. I can try it though
`env-local-crafting.json` looks good (the db_params are in there)
Interestingly, all your services are failing in the same way (job-service as well)
@Ganan Prabaharan you are way behind master. rebase :slightly_smiling_face:
